title: Routing4Safety
subtitle: Because everybody deserves to come home

splash.splashContent:
Welcome to Routing4Safety!






Here are three things to get you started:


1) Begin by choosing your mode of travel and specifying the current conditions. You can enter your desired start and end locations to route yourself along a safe path that avoids high-risk collision areas. 

2) To understand more about collisions in your city, explore the infographics based on historical data or enable the emerging hot spot layers to identify future trends.

3) To report new collisions, use the "Report a Collision" button to easily fill out a map-based survey.
